      "writtenOn": "2026-06-17T18:28:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Technically speaking, D-Bus NotAllowed is not semantically equivalent to Redfish InsufficientPrivilege.\n\nThe bmcweb gateway strictly validates AssignedPrivileges against the Redfish PrivilegeRegistry. \n\nIn contrast, NotAllowed indicates a backend policy restriction.\nThe exact match in the MessageRegistry is ResourceCannotBeDeleted as alternative.\n\nReference - https://redfish.dmtf.org/registries/Base.1.23.0.json",
      "revId": "d5d79978d67ce70d28d7ccfb65c39e17bea2088f",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
